channel.title: [PI] Rampage X [PI]
channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i584.photobucket.com/albums/ss285/Nightmare97/Untitled-1-1.jpg[/img][/center]
[center]So basically i'm releasing this source because my whole community fell apart. It was fun while It lasted, and maybe some of you guys will get some use out of the source. This source was known as Rune Verfix and was a decent source, though I made alot of changes and tried to make it better.
First of all I want to list the credits:
-Acrodox -ExtremeX-Scape™ <-- Tremendous help couldn't of done it without him.
Ok, so here goes some changes/things I added:
[color=orange]-Some new portals -Pk Box -PvP Points, and PvP point shop -[b]Follow[/b] -Fixed slayer -Fixed Exp Lock -Fixed Equip Manager -Decent Exp Rate -::restart (good for dropbox, all you have to do is compile and ::restart updates everything) -Staff Zone -Donor shop and Donor zone -Fixed Woodcutting -Skill-capes {Work in a ghetto way} (click skill cape emote, then zombie hand and it will work) -A few more things I can remember off the top of my head, but Ill update[/center] [hr]
[center][b] ~~~FEATURES~~~[/b][/center]
[center]
KBD CORP BEAST K- Queen High-scores Activity shop UNIQUE Home 100% Slayer Rune crafting Economy Good exp rate Skiller Clothes Shop Ancients Lunar Thieving Multiple Pk Zones GwD (not 100% :( ) Saradomin Sword and Spec Activity points (gain by killing bosses, pking, and doing slayer) EXP - Locking/Unlocking Skill Restarting Dragon Skimmy Spec 100% Assault Mini game Fighter torso and defenders Pest Control 100% whip spec Barrows Gloves Great Pk Zones EQUIPMENT BONUS BOX WORKS Colored Whips Vestas Statius's Morrigans Bandos God-swords Colored Dark Bows Spirit Shields Super Stable and MUCH MUCH MORE
[hr]
To be honest I don't expect this to be a great release because I would of like more time to develop and add cool features in it, but if I don't release this now, ill never release it. Here is some [b]pictures[/b].
